Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO WAYS AND MEANS

Title: Clarifies that certain documents attached to real estate tax returns are not considered tax returns for certain secrecy purposes
Summary: Clarifies that certain documents attached to real estate tax returns are not considered tax returns for certain secrecy purposes.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law, in relation to clarifying that certain documents attached to real estate tax returns are not considered tax returns for certain secrecy purposes
